================================================================================
KEY FINDINGS
================================================================================

Average F1 gain from hierarchical fallback: +0.0499
Average recall gain: +0.0422

This demonstrates that the hierarchical schema provides:
1. Graceful degradation when fine-grained types are confused
2. Higher recall for entity boundary detection
3. A foundation for taxonomy extension without retraining
